What Israel wants this man dead.

00:00:14.681 --> 00:00:15.949
Yayha Sinwar

00:00:15.949 --> 00:00:17.817
The leader of Hamas in Gaza.

00:00:17.817 --> 00:00:22.022
In the face of evil in the end

00:00:22.088 --> 00:00:22.922
is Yayha Sinwar

00:00:22.922 --> 00:00:25.458
Well, that man is in our sights.

00:00:25.458 --> 00:00:28.661
All his team are and will get to them.

00:00:28.728 --> 00:00:30.830
He was first convicted in 1988

00:00:30.830 --> 00:00:32.732
for the murder of two Israeli soldiers

00:00:32.732 --> 00:00:34.300
and four Palestinians

00:00:34.300 --> 00:00:37.570
suspected of collaboration with Israel.

00:00:37.670 --> 00:00:39.005
And he spent two decades

00:00:39.005 --> 00:00:42.575
in an Israeli prison studying his enemy,

00:00:42.642 --> 00:00:43.743
the founder of Hamas

00:00:43.743 --> 00:00:45.412
internal security force.

00:00:45.412 --> 00:00:46.513
He had hunted alleged

00:00:46.513 --> 00:00:49.649
collaborators with zeal and

00:00:49.716 --> 00:00:51.418
brothers and was among the movement's

00:00:51.418 --> 00:00:52.385
biggest prizes

00:00:52.385 --> 00:00:53.319
when over a thousand

00:00:53.319 --> 00:00:54.788
Palestinian prisoners

00:00:54.788 --> 00:00:56.656
were released in 2011.

00:00:56.656 --> 00:00:58.191
For Gilad Shalit,

00:00:58.191 --> 00:01:00.894
an Israeli soldier held hostage in Gaza

00:01:00.894 --> 00:01:04.631
for five years, he said, 

00:01:04.697 --> 00:01:05.598
there is no doubt

00:01:05.598 --> 00:01:07.567
that this is a nationalistic moment,

00:01:07.567 --> 00:01:08.968
par excellence.

00:01:08.968 --> 00:01:11.371
It is one of the big strategic monuments

00:01:11.371 --> 00:01:14.340
in the history of our cause.

00:01:14.474 --> 00:01:16.242
He quickly became head of Hamas

00:01:16.242 --> 00:01:17.377
military wing

00:01:17.377 --> 00:01:18.878
and on election to the Gaza

00:01:18.878 --> 00:01:20.980
leadership in 2017,

00:01:20.980 --> 00:01:22.382
effectively abolished

00:01:22.382 --> 00:01:24.184
its civilian branch,

00:01:24.184 --> 00:01:26.386
ostracized by Egypt over its support

00:01:26.386 --> 00:01:27.854
for political Islam.

00:01:27.854 --> 00:01:30.256
He repaired friendships with Cairo

00:01:30.256 --> 00:01:30.723
and built

00:01:30.723 --> 00:01:32.192
regional relationships

00:01:32.192 --> 00:01:34.260
that entrenched Hamas power.

00:01:34.260 --> 00:01:35.595
It really needed to have

00:01:35.595 --> 00:01:37.263
also good relations

00:01:37.263 --> 00:01:40.733
with the key Arab state that also shares

00:01:40.733 --> 00:01:43.069
the only era border with the Gaza Strip

00:01:43.069 --> 00:01:47.240
and with Iran that could supply Hamas

00:01:47.240 --> 00:01:51.211
with military and logistical support.

00:01:51.444 --> 00:01:53.313
Iran has poured military support

00:01:53.313 --> 00:01:54.514
into Hamas under him,

00:01:54.514 --> 00:01:56.649
and Qatar has been a major backer

00:01:56.649 --> 00:01:58.451
of civilian projects.

00:01:58.451 --> 00:02:00.453
He was soon in Israel's crosshairs.

00:02:00.453 --> 00:02:01.754
Quite literally,

00:02:01.754 --> 00:02:05.492
the IDF tried to kill him in May 20, 21.

00:02:05.558 --> 00:02:08.561
Ten days later, he laid out his strategy.

00:02:08.661 --> 00:02:10.130
He said

00:02:10.230 --> 00:02:11.097
if the world doesn't

00:02:11.097 --> 00:02:13.633
take action to stop it, meaning Israel,

00:02:13.633 --> 00:02:15.201
there will be a religious war

00:02:15.201 --> 00:02:16.936
in the region.

00:02:16.936 --> 00:02:18.471
And he soon appeared in Gaza

00:02:18.471 --> 00:02:20.206
alongside Egypt's intelligence

00:02:20.206 --> 00:02:21.875
chief, Abbas Kamel.

00:02:21.875 --> 00:02:22.575
For us,

00:02:22.575 --> 00:02:25.645
the US is now relying on Egypt and Qatar

00:02:25.879 --> 00:02:26.913
as key players

00:02:26.913 --> 00:02:28.281
to try to secure the safe

00:02:28.281 --> 00:02:32.018
release of Hamas's 200 captives.

00:02:32.085 --> 00:02:33.953
Their main point of contact

00:02:33.953 --> 00:02:36.756
is likely Sinwar.

00:02:36.756 --> 00:02:38.024
unless Israel fulfills

00:02:38.024 --> 00:02:40.460
its promise to kill them.

00:02:40.460 --> 00:02:42.328
Sam Kiley, CNN.

00:02:42.328 --> 00:02:45.298
The move of

