that civilians were targeted.

00:05:55.388 --> 00:05:56.622
He denies that the

00:05:56.622 --> 00:06:00.793
women and children were slaughtered.

00:06:00.893 --> 00:06:02.261
He did say some things,

00:06:02.261 --> 00:06:04.163
which we found unconvincing about that.

00:06:04.163 --> 00:06:04.397
Yeah.

00:06:04.397 --> 00:06:05.798
He said, you know, after the Hamas

00:06:05.798 --> 00:06:06.866
fighters came in.

00:06:06.866 --> 00:06:08.701
Others came in afterwards.

00:06:08.701 --> 00:06:09.769
And it was those others

00:06:09.769 --> 00:06:11.371
who did these misdeeds.

00:06:11.371 --> 00:06:12.038
Yeah, that's true.

00:06:12.038 --> 00:06:13.573
I didn't find that very convincing.

00:06:13.573 --> 00:06:14.073
He's certainly

00:06:14.073 --> 00:06:15.208
not the first military leader

00:06:15.208 --> 00:06:19.278
