from what he said that they do not.

00:06:29.922 --> 00:06:31.324
You know, obviously this is a war.

00:06:31.324 --> 00:06:32.859
There's lots of misinformation.

00:06:32.859 --> 00:06:34.861
But he was he seemed very candid.

00:06:34.861 --> 00:06:36.162
We said, you know what,

00:06:36.162 --> 00:06:37.263
if Hezbollah enters this, well,

00:06:37.263 --> 00:06:38.698
what if it becomes a regional conflict?

00:06:38.698 --> 00:06:39.932
