if only it could

00:06:41.868 --> 00:06:42.869
become a regional conflict.

00:06:42.869 --> 00:06:43.870
We would love that.

00:06:43.870 --> 00:06:45.905
But we don't see any sign of it.

00:06:45.905 --> 00:06:48.241
Hezbollah is going to more or less abide

00:06:48.241 --> 00:06:51.244
by its cease fire with Israel, he said.

00:06:51.277 --> 00:06:54.046
And he did not expect this war to expand

00:06:54.046 --> 00:06:57.850
on that other front.

00:06:57.917 --> 00:06:59.318
David Kirkpatrick, thank you so much.

00:06:59.318 --> 00:06:59.819
It's good to have you on

00:06:59.819 --> 00:07:00.453
the program again.

